title: RealArcade - Samantha Swift and the Golden Touch - New HOG Puzzl
description:
Samantha Swift and the Golden Touch  156.25 MB


When Samantha's new benefactor asks her to track down Alexander the Great's Scroll of Wealth, the opportunity seems too good to be true: searching for the scroll while collecting artifacts to display in her Museum of Secrets Lost.


Things are never that straightforward, though. Little does Samantha know that the secret brotherhood is watching her every move and she'll have to do a lot more digging to find the true treasure, which taks her on a journey to unravel the mystery of King Midas' Golden Touch.
